        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>New design hydraulic brake rotors are available as replacement rotors for all vehicles equipped
                    with pin slide hydraulic brakes and ABS. The new part number replacement rotors have an improved
                    tone ring that is more resistant to corrosion. The new part number rotors are direct replacements
                    for the old part number rotors. Service is directed to use these rotors on all hydraulic pin slide
                    brakes with ABS.
                </para>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
